      "content": "but that's just easy for someone to say. what does \"worth\" even mean when you've lost everything that gave you purpose? there's no coming back from this kind of social death. the damage is permanent. it feels like i'm just existing in a void where everything i used to care about is just... dead. i don't see the point in trying to \"find a path\" when there's nothing left to walk on. it just feels so much more logical to just stop fighting it.",
